events.name: Alabama Crimson Tide at Florida Gators

headlines.description: Alabama showed off all its weapons in the Southeastern Conference championship game.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 1 Alabama romps past Florida 54-16 in SEC title game

events.name: Clemson Tigers at Virginia Tech Hokies

headlines.description: Deshaun Watson bolstered his Heisman Trophy candidacy by passing for three touchdowns and running for two more to lead third-ranked Clemson to a 42-35 victory over No. 19 Virginia Tech in the Atl
headlines.shortLinkText: Watson accounts for 5 TDs, Clemson beats Virginia Tech 42-35

events.name: Wisconsin Badgers at Penn State Nittany Lions

headlines.description: Trace McSorley threw four touchdown passes Saturday night and No. 7 Penn State stunned No. 6 Wisconsin 38-31, rallying from a 21-point first-half deficit.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 7 Penn St. rallies to beat No. 6 Wisconsin 38-31

events.name: Oklahoma State Cowboys at Oklahoma Sooners

headlines.description: Baker Mayfield passed for 288 yards and three touchdowns, and No. 9 Oklahoma defeated No. 10 Oklahoma State 38-20 on Saturday in a matchup that decided the Big 12 champion.
headlines.shortLinkText: Mayfield, Oklahoma top Oklahoma St. 38-20 to win Big 12

events.name: Baylor Bears at West Virginia Mountaineers

headlines.description: Skyler Howard threw two touchdown passes and ran for another score, and No. 14 West Virginia held on for a 24-21 victory over Baylor on Saturday night in their Big 12 regular-season finale.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 16 West Virginia beats Baylor 24-21 to get to 10 wins

headlines.description: Phillip Walker threw two touchdown passes, Temple's defense stuffed Navy's running game, and the Owls claimed their first American Athletic Conference title with a 34-10 victory Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Temple silences No. 19 Navy, wins AAC crown

events.name: Kansas State Wildcats at TCU Horned Frogs

headlines.description: Jesse Ertz ran for a career-high 170 yards with a touchdown and threw an 83-yard scoring pass as Kansas State ended its regular season with a 30-6 win at TCU on a drizzly Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ertz runs for career-high 170 yards as K-State tops TCU 30-6

events.name: Troy Trojans at Georgia Southern Eagles

headlines.description: Kevin Ellison threw for two touchdowns and ran for two more and Georgia Southern beat Troy 28-24 on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ellison directs Georgia Southern to upset over Troy 28-24

video.headline: Johnson's 64-yard catch and run holds as winning TD

events.name: Louisiana Tech Bulldogs at Western Kentucky Hilltoppers

headlines.description: Anthony Wales rushed for 209 yards and four touchdowns, Mike White threw for 421 and three more scores and Western Kentucky defeated Louisiana Tech 58-44 on Saturday in the Conference USA champio
headlines.shortLinkText: W Kentucky wins C-USA in shootout 58-44 over Louisiana Tech

video.headline: Anthony Wales goes untouched for fifth TD

events.name: New Mexico State Aggies at South Alabama Jaguars

headlines.description: Xavier Johnson rushed for 154 yards and three touchdowns, both career bests, and South Alabama became bowl eligible with a 35-28 win over New Mexico State on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Johnson scores 3 TDs, helps make South Alabama bowl eligible

video.headline: Xavier Johnson extends South Alabama's lead late with 35-yard TD

events.name: New Hampshire Wildcats at James Madison Dukes

notes.headline: NCAA DIVISION I FOOTBALL CHAMPIONSHIP - SECOND ROUND

headlines.description: James Madison quarterback Bryan Schor was sidelined by injury for the last game and a half of the regular season, but at least it was to his non-throwing shoulder.
headlines.shortLinkText: JMU rolls past UNH 55-22 in 2nd round

events.name: Louisiana Ragin' Cajuns at Louisiana Monroe Warhawks

headlines.description: Elijah McGuire ran for 110 yards and a touchdown, and Louisiana-Lafayette returned two fumbles for scores to beat Louisiana-Monroe 30-3 in the rain on Saturday.

video.headline: Trev Miller goes 73 yards for scoop-and-score TD

events.name: Georgia State Panthers at Idaho Vandals

headlines.description: Matt Linehan threw three touchdown passes and the defense forced six turnovers to lead Idaho to a 37-12 win over Georgia State on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Idaho forces 6 turnovers to defeat Georgia State 37-12

video.headline: Blocked punt turns into Idaho touchdown

events.name: Arkansas State Red Wolves at Texas State Bobcats

headlines.shortLinkText: Hansen's 2 TDs carry Arkansas State past Texas State, 36-14

events.name: San Diego State Aztecs at Wyoming Cowboys

venue.fullName: Jonah Field at War Memorial Stadium

headlines.description: Rashaad Penny rushed for 117 yards and two touchdowns, and Donnel Pumphrey added 110 yards and one TD as San Diego State beat Wyoming 27-24 on Saturday for its second consecutive Mountain West Co
headlines.shortLinkText: Penny, Pumphrey lead San Diego State to Mountain West title
